        "title": "The Hundred 2026 (Women's)",
        "shortDescription": "The first-ever player auction for Women’s Hundred 2026 goes underway in an IPL-style format with up to four overseas players per squad.  A star-studded marquee list including Deepti Sharma, Sophie Devine, Beth Mooney, and Tammy Beaumont among others will headline the 178 players going under the hammer. Tune in to catch all the action, LIVE & exclusively on Sony LIV",
